      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification test suite and version control consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v2022R2 used with documented QA procedures, regression test suite, and version-controlled case files. All SQA requirements for MRL 2 are satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
