      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence study required; discretization error must be quantified and shown to be below 5% of the hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-level grid refinement study conducted (3.2M, 8.7M, and 22.1M cells). Richardson extrapolation yields discretization error of 1.8% on the normalized hemolysis index, exceeding MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
