      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this device class; FDA interlaboratory data provides sufficient sample characterization.",
      "rationale": "FDA interlaboratory study provides multi-laboratory, multi-sample experimental baseline. Separate test sample characterization not required at MRL 2 for Class II device."
    },
