      "rationale": "Simulation inputs matched to experimental nominal conditions. Formal equivalency assessment of input parameters not required at MRL 2. Differences in fluid rheology between blood analog and in vivo blood are acknowledged as a known modeling assumption consistent with FDA guidance."
