    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device. Uncertainty quantification via comprehensive Monte Carlo analysis across all 13 model inputs demonstrates that RH < 1 with 97.3% probability across the CPB operating envelope, providing sufficient confidence for the regulatory submission decision. The credibility package is judged adequate to support the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions.",
